                ol
                    li
                      | To be simple,only
                      span(style="color:red;") *
                      | &nbsp items is required, ignore other fields you can
                    li Only <strong>Summary</strong> field is required currently, recommand fill your detail in <strong>Description</strong> field
              br
              br
